7%2FScreenshot_2017-10-14-10-31-46.png&h=a28273a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em>肥鳩大隻連解讀中文&ldquo;你照鏡咪知囉懵撚&rdquo;哩句句子都有困難，自己柒左仲要周圍話俾人知，不如學好d中文先出黎教人啦懵撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </em></span></span>"},{"pid":"55483845ad5ae1268d3267920e7ab57d14f7072b","tid":555044,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:16:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>當本癲狗將肥鳩大隻既身型貼出黎俾大家睇，肥鳩大隻亦不甘示弱，馬上自貼作補充，自爆身型肥到漢堡包一樣:</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/4xojdei69/Screenshot_2017-12-28-10-57-23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2F4xojdei69%2FScreenshot_2017-12-28-10-57-23.png&h=2929b634&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>由此可見，肥鳩大隻哩隻食屎狗被本癲狗教化以後，有時都幾老實</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}